'''俄羅斯遠東號船難'''，是指發生在2015年4月1日晚間（[[UTC+8|UTC+8]]為2日清晨）的一起沉船事故。根據俄羅斯媒體報導，一艘於[[堪察加半島|堪察加半島]]旁的[[鄂霍次克海|鄂霍次克海]]作業的[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]籍[[漁船|漁船]]遠東號（Dalniy Vostok，音譯為“达利尼·沃斯托克”号），疑似因為撞上浮冰沉沒<ref name=voa>{{cite news|title=俄罗斯一艘拖网渔船沉没 数十人丧生|url=http://m.voachinese.com/a/russia-trawler-20150402/2703702.html|accessdate=2015-04-02|newspaper=美國之音|date=2015-04-02|archive-date=2015-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409125741/http://m.voachinese.com/a/russia-trawler-20150402/2703702.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這艘船共有132名船員，其中78人是俄羅斯籍，其餘船員分別來自[[缅甸|缅甸]]、[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]、[[拉脱维亚|拉脱维亚]]和[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]]等國<ref>{{cite web|title=Dozens dead as trawler sinks in Russia’s far east|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/04/01/dozens-dead-as-trawler-sinks-in-russias-far-east/|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2015-04-01|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402201000/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/04/01/dozens-dead-as-trawler-sinks-in-russias-far-east/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。已知有63人獲救，54人死亡，15人失蹤<ref>{{cite web|title=Russian trawler sinks in Sea of Okhotsk, 54 crew members dead|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/russian-trawler-sinks-in-sea-of-okhotsk-54-crew-members-dead-1.3018830|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2015-04-01|archive-date=2019-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190313102649/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/russian-trawler-sinks-in-sea-of-okhotsk-54-crew-members-dead-1.3018830}}</ref>。

